.TH paused
.SH NAME
paused - server response to inform the client about the game pause.
.SH DESCRIPTION
The close request is sent to a client to inform whether the game hosted on the server is paused or not.
.br
Response contains boolean value, true or false.
.br
It is sent to all connected clients along with an update reponse.
.SH JSON EXAMPLE
.nf
{
  "paused": true
}
.SH SEE ALSO
responses, game, request/pause